OEM: [[Arcadyan]] WG9117C22-ASU (EU) {{see also|ASUS RT-N56U B1|Arcadyan}} *Simultaneous Dual-Band, Gigabit Ethernet :2x USB 2.0 ports for Printers and Storage :Android (3G/4G) USB Tethering <!-- (Important: USB Debugging must be off on the android device) -->
===Overview=== *Dual-band for lag-free entertainment *5x faster Gigabit internet surfing with hardware NAT *Powerful Online Multitasking at up to 300,000 Data Sessions *Twin USB ports enable multi-role usability
===Specifications=== *Product Segment: N600 enhanced :Wi-Fi performance: 300 + 300 Mbps *Operating Frequency: 2.4GHz / 5GHz *Antenna: :2.4GHz: 2x 3.8dBi internal antenna :5GHz: 3x 5.1dBi internal antenna *Memory: Flash: 8MB, RAM: 128MB *Ports: 2x USB 2.0 :WAN: 1x RJ45 GbE (10/100/1000 BaseT) :LAN: 4x RJ45 GbE (10/100/1000 BaseT) *Power Supply: :AC Input : 110~240V (50/60Hz) :DC Output : 19V with max. 1.58A current *Dimensions: 172mm x 145mm x 60mm (WxDxH) *Weight: 330g
